Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//正文
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.46,0:01:02.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了  最重要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不告訴龍峰同學呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.97,0:01:04.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得很好玩？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.41,0:01:06.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊騙我  那邊又討好他…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.21,0:01:09.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經不想逃避了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.56,0:01:11.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正臣你是沒法逃離過去的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.89,0:01:15.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在這樣煩惱也是和過去有關的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.06,0:01:19.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要恨的話就去恨下命令的紀田正臣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.94,0:01:22.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DOLLARS要消失
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OP
