Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.37,0:01:55.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俄羅斯壽司  俄羅斯壽司 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.27,0:01:58.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃又便宜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.29,0:02:00.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥來份怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.24,0:02:02.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位社長
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.42,0:02:31.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  俄羅斯壽司店
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.66,0:02:36.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道該打給誰好就打到你這邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.81,0:02:39.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.21,0:02:43.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想告訴你們那個人所想的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.55,0:02:48.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波江小姐  這種情況叫什麼來著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.98,0:02:53.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將軍？checkmate？還是中大獎了？喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.93,0:02:58.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼不在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
